        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "太史公曰：五帝、三代之記，尚矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Grand Historian said: Five Emperors, Three Dynasties records, far ancient.",
              "idiomatic": "The Grand Historian said: The records of the Five Emperors and Three Dynasties go far back in time.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "自殷以前諸侯不可得而譜，周以來乃頗可著。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "From Yin before feudal lords cannot obtained and genealogized, Zhou since then considerably can recorded.",
              "idiomatic": "Before the Yin dynasty, the feudal lords cannot be genealogically charted. Since the Zhou, they can be considerably recorded.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "孔子因史文次春秋，紀元年，正時日月，蓋其詳哉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Confucius followed historical texts arranged Spring Autumn, recorded first year, corrected seasons days months, indeed its detailed.",
              "idiomatic": "Confucius followed the historical texts and arranged the Spring and Autumn Annals, recording the first year, correcting the seasons, days, and months - indeed how detailed!",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "至於序尚書則略，無年月；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "As for arranging the Documents of Antiquity then brief, no years months;",
              "idiomatic": "As for arranging the Documents of Antiquity, it was brief, with no years or months;",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "或頗有，然多闕，不可錄。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Some considerably had, yet many missing, cannot recorded.",
              "idiomatic": "Some considerably had them, yet many were missing and could not be recorded.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "故疑則傳疑，蓋其慎也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Therefore doubt then transmit doubt, indeed its cautious.",
              "idiomatic": "Therefore when in doubt, transmit doubt - indeed how cautious!",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "The Grand Historian said: The records of the Five Emperors and Three Dynasties go far back in time. Before the Yin dynasty, the feudal lords cannot be genealogically charted. Since the Zhou, they can be considerably recorded. Confucius followed the historical texts and arranged the Spring and Autumn Annals, recording the first year, correcting the seasons, days, and months - indeed how detailed! As for arranging the Documents of Antiquity, it was brief, with no years or months; Some considerably had them, yet many were missing and could not be recorded. Therefore when in doubt, transmit doubt - indeed how cautious!",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": "AI",
          "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "余讀諜記，黃帝以來皆有年數。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "I read secret records, Yellow Emperor since all have year numbers.",
              "idiomatic": "I read secret records - since the Yellow Emperor, all have year counts.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "稽其歷譜諜終始五德之傳，古文咸不同，乖異。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Check their calendar genealogies secret records beginning end five virtues transmission, ancient texts all different, divergent.",
              "idiomatic": "Checking their calendar genealogies and secret records of the beginning and end of the five virtues transmission, the ancient texts are all different and divergent.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "夫子之弗論次其年月，豈虛哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Master not discussed arranged their years months, how vain!",
              "idiomatic": "The Master did not discuss and arrange their years and months - how could it be in vain!",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "於是以五帝系諜、尚書集世紀黃帝以連山訖共和為世表。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "Thereupon with Five Emperors genealogical records, Documents of Antiquity collected century Yellow Emperor with Lianshan until Gonghe as generation table.",
              "idiomatic": "Thereupon, using the Five Emperors genealogical records and the Documents of Antiquity collected century, from the Yellow Emperor through Lianshan until Gonghe as the generation table.",
              "translator": "AI",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "I read secret records - since the Yellow Emperor, all have year counts. Checking their calendar genealogies and secret records of the beginning and end of the five virtues transmission, the ancient texts are all different and divergent. The Master did not discuss and arrange their years and months - how could it be in vain! Thereupon, using the Five Emperors genealogical records and the Documents of Antiquity collected century, from the Yellow Emperor through Lianshan until Gonghe as the generation table.",
          "idiomatic": null,
          "translator": "AI",
          "model": "grok-code-fast-1"
        }
